HEADWORD: Catchwork
<hw>Catch"work`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A work or
artificial water-course for throwing water on lands that lie on the
slopes of hills; a catchdrain.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

